This is a prime example of useless use of cat. Heredoc already means &quot;pass this as stdin&quot;, there&#x27;s no need to pipe it. Your example without cat:<p><pre><code>    curl http://localhost -d @- <<REQUEST_BODY
    {
      &quot;from&quot; : 0,
      &quot;size&quot; : 40
    }
    REQUEST_BODY</code></pre>
